(26018, 'Rheumarene 50mg 20 tab.', 'رومارين 50مجم 20 اقراص', '', '14', 'Diclofenac sodium', 'Sedico', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Nsaid.acetic acid derivatives', '50mg', 'Diclofenac is indicated for use in the treatment of pain and inflammation from varying sources including inflammatory conditions such as osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, and ankylosing spondylitis, as well as injury-related inflammation due to surgery and physical trauma. It is often used in combination with [misoprostol] as a gastro-protective agent in patients with high risk of developing NSAID-induced ulcers.', '6221042016024', '', 1446, '2022-12-08', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
