(19436, 'Fruzex 40mg 12 tab.', 'فروزكس 40 مجم 12 قرص', '', '3', 'Furosemide', 'Misr', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Diuretic.loop', '40mg', 'Furosemide is indicated for the treatment of edema associated with congestive heart failure, cirrhosis of the liver, and renal disease, including the nephrotic syndrome, in adults and pediatric patients.[L7958] 
Oral furosemide is indicated alone for the management of mild to moderate hypertension or severe hypertension in combination with other antihypertensive medications.[L9659]
Intravenous furosemide is indicated as adjunctive therapy in acute pulmonary edema when a rapid onset of diuresis is desired.[L7958]
Subcutaneous furosemide is indicated for the treatment of congestion due to fluid overload in adults with NYHA Class II/III chronic heart failure. This drug formulation is not indicated for emergency situations or in patients with acute pulmonary edema.[L43408]', '', '', 837, '2022-07-30', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(17203, 'Delestra rectal oint. 30 gm', 'ديليسترا مرهم 30 جم', '', '25', 'Cinchocaine+policresulen', 'Sabaa', 'Oint', 'مرهم', '', 'Haemorrhoids', '30 gm', 'about cinchocaine an amide derivative most potent and toxic long-acting local anesthetics a local anaesthetic mechanism of action of cinchocaine cinchocaine is a local anesthetic. it works by blocking the pathway of pain signals along nerves. it inhibits', '', '', 1384, '2022-07-16', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
